Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:09.69,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:19.89,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,…gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,…but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I’ve made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.45,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:06.92,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:14.19,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:20.97,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,…a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair… Don’t you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:28.33,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:05.52,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The Nearby War
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:21.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,That wraps up\Nthe patrol flight schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:28.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you authorized\Nmobilization of Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:34.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re still flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:38.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said we couldn’t gauge\NSimoun chemistry otherwise, Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:43.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve had enough!\NYou’re amazing, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,So can we…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,We haven’t done a Ri Majon yet.\NLet’s try the Ray Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look at Aer go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:09.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s too complicated! I’m confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:19.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just wait… Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:12.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is currently grounded\Nuntil its newest members arrive…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,…Sibylla Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we don’t practice,\Nit’ll be tough when trouble comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:23.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then use Similes.\NAfter you’ve received permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer! Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why’d you pray without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:38.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was a battle drill, not a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you scolding us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:47.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re not even\Nthe regina of Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:52.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,The regina of our chor,\NNeviril, is indisposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, I’m stepping in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:59.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh? Don’t tell me\Nthat you and Sibylla Aurea…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,…have that kind of special relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:22.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer! You forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:30.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,The kiss of gratitude. After exiting\Nthe Simoun, Tempus Spatium…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I couldn’t care less about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you hate doing it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:46.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Waporif, I’m sorry. We might’ve\Ngotten you in trouble too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:50.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s our job to launch\NSimouns when sibyllae request it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,How cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:00.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,She’s a child. You needn’t tease her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:02.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tease? Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:09.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you know what? Flying with\Nthat girl was simply wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:22.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was amazing, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:26.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which Ri Majon\Nwere you trying before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, don’t do anything like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:34.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why not? Are you all okay\Nwith the way things are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:39.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,When will they put Chor Tempest\Non duty to relieve the other chors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,At this rate…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:46.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,If that happens, we can go back\Nto being normal Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:50.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Offering prayers and waiting\Nfor our time to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,The day I choose to become male.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can hardly wait, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:01.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m planning to choose\Nthe male gender myself, Alty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,You all think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:08.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,That it’s fine to not\Ngo into battle anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:13.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s Chor Rubor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:17.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Making a safe return\Nagain today, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:29.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,You tried to do\Nthe Ray Ri Majon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are a genius after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:36.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can’t even do\Na simple thing like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:39.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this really\Nis Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:46.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that how you feel too, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:50.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,That it doesn’t matter as long\Nas you don’t go into battle anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:54.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,How could anyone want to go to war?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:57.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, we are merely…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:08:02.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,…fulfilling our duties as priestesses\Nprotecting Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:05.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then you fulfill that duty too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:11.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me make myself clear.\NAer, you and I will never be a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m Vura of Chor Rubor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:29.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’ll be roommates starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:34.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that right? I’m Aer of Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re an auriga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:40.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am too.\NSay, has that Neviril always been…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:46.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since Chor Tempest is off active duty,\Nmy chor’s been split into two units…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,…doing patrol flights night and day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:52.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,We don’t have the luxury\Nof lazing around like you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:09.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I bet I can fly in a way\Nthat would satisfy even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone’s in\Nthe cafeteria at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:30.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:34.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s all right. I grabbed dinner for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s not it…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:39.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a pain in the butt…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, your half.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Also…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:02.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which Ri Majon first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:04.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t know…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:11.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Silver Ri Majon… I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:15.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah? That’s a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:19.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if we’re going to,\Nlet’s do it when we find the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:22.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re going into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:27.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we do, they won’t be able\Nto ground our chor anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn’t that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:31.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:33.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:11:00.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,The new recruits in Chor Caput\Nare out on patrol tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why’s it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:05.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:10.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then they’ve got info on the enemy.\NLet’s make sure the area’s secure first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just one unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m in luck. This will be my last…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:44.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,It has to be Aer!\NAnd with Rimone this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:47.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone? But that’s my pair…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,She rejected me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:53.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s not really\Na matter of being rejected…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:58.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another unauthorized flight?\NI wish my chor had free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:02.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,This means the end of\NChor Tempest. We’re going to be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:04.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Should we notify the dux?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:08.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we don’t get them,\Nwe’re all accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don’t we leave them alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:15.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they want to fly,\Nwe should let them fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’ll be back by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:21.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can’t move\Nthe Arcus Prima right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:26.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of\Npriestess is this Aer girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:30.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,All that is certain…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,…is that she has a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,A reason for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:57.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s a fake…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:01.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Damn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:16.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s right.\NWe’re both Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:21.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it’s true when they say that young\Ngirls fly the Simouns in Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:30.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The disease is eating\Naway at our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:34.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are in need of new technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:38.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,The secret of Simouns,\Nhidden by Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we can acquire that…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:43.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,…we can bid farewell to\Ntechnology that pollutes the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:05.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I did it… I’ve taken a Simoun…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:08.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m not going to retire from the military!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:12.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Glory to Shoukoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:20.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:26.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,You soldiers from Shoukoku aren’t\Nprotected by Tempus Spatium!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:30.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Only priestesses who haven’t gone\Nto the Spring can operate Simouns!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:34.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Only us, people who haven’t\Ndecided on a gender yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:39.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me how to fly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:42.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:27.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,We retake the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:29.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t talk so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:34.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,He can’t understand our words anyway.\NShoukoku wants the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:39.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since only Simouns fly freely through\Nthe skies. But we can’t hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:47.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of my friends\Nhave gone to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m the only one\Nin my village who hasn’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:53.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don’t you want to go, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:59.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I’m not sure. Whether I want\Nto become a man or stay a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:03.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you go, they say Onasia\Nchooses if you haven’t decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:07.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Having someone else choose\Nis worse! No, I don’t want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:09.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t afford to make\Nmistakes in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:13.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll become the best\NSimoun sibylla of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:18.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all, as long as I fly a Simoun,\NI won’t have to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:25.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me, young ladies…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,How does it feel?\NNot to be a man or woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don’t understand, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:40.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was turned male via medicine\Nand surgery right when I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:43.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s the way things\Nare done in Shoukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:46.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s why I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Being born in a female body…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:54.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and then being able to choose\Nwhether to become a man or woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:56.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,How does that feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:06.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think that man is ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:57.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go! Fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:18:00.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, fly! What’s wrong, demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:02.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why won’t you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:11.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry, young ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:14.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t hand this over\Nto you. It’s mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:20.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I can just take this back,\Nmy country will usher in a new era.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:22.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,The skies will clear…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I’m going to…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:39.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like I said, you can’t fly a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:44.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,His comrades might come for him.\NIn Shoukoku aircraft…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:50.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won’t let him have it.\NHe’ll never take the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Help me get him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need to get back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,He’s all stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go! Let go, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:42.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t. It’ll break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:50.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sure someone\Nwill come looking for us…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then we can…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:52.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:57.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,We don’t know when the enemy will\Ncome. We have to take off right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:20:02.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,And we can’t ever report that we\Nnearly got captured by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:08.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,If only these hands on\Nthe flight stick could be removed…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can’t be helped…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:15.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, you can\Ngo over there till I’m done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ow…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:07.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone! Help me carry him, Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:10.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you awake, Rimone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:12.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:52.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess I made trouble for you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:56.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,As an apology,\Nwe’ll clean it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don’t have to do that, Sibylla Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:01.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s fine. We want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:15.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Taking on the task of\Ncleaning the Simoun themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:18.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’re starting to recognize\Nthat they’re priestesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:20.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:27.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:29.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,For getting you so dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:47.82,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds…\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:52.06,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:59.13,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon’t be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:06.93,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart’s overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:19.61,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,“I want to get closer to you.”\N“I want to feel your pulse.”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:24.79,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:28.80,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:32.77,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart’s desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:38.06,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can’t reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.70,0:23:44.22,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:47.68,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:53.32,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.32,0:23:59.48,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to “now” the way it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.67,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:12.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Will Dominüra be up\Nto the task of guiding Rimone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.67,0:24:16.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:17.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,White Loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:20.02,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}White Loneliness
